Convert a Truetype font into WOFF2<pre><code>cd RetroTxt
pnpm run font fontname.ttf fontname.woff2
</code></pre> <p>Tip for Windows</p> <p>Windows users may need to update the font script in the <code>package.json</code> file.</p> OriginalEdit <pre><code>"scripts": {
  "font": "woff2_compress.js"
},
</code></pre> <pre><code>"scripts": {
  "font": "woff2_compress.js.cmd"
},
</code></pre>
